  "body": "### Version of Hardhat\n\n2.12.6\n\n### What happened?\n\nDuplicate of #2942.\r\n\r\nAfter using the task \"verify:verify\" sometimes my scripts hang and I have to kill them manually.\r\n\r\n`contracts/Foo.sol:FooContract at 0x...abc for verification on the block explorer. Waiting for verification result...`\r\n[and hangs here for a few hours]\r\n\r\nI think there should be a timeout.\r\n\r\n@nomiclabs/hardhat-etherscan@3.1.5\n\n### Minimal reproduction steps\n\n```ts\r\nimport { run } from \"hardhat\";\r\n\r\nawait run(\"verify:verify\", {\r\n  \"0xb8361A958E30FeF0A18f509cfe899946E9FFb853\",\r\n  [],\r\n  \"contracts/Foo.sol:FooContract\",\r\n});\r\n```\n\n### Search terms\n\n_No response_",
